# dex-specific exclusions (gitignore syntax).
# Layered ON TOP of .gitignore: things here are kept in git but kept
# out of the dex index. Use this for paths that are real source in git
# but bloat the index or distort summarizer/retrieval signal.

# Benchmark run outputs — large auto-generated JSON dumps that
# dominate file_summary / package_summary signal without representing
# any production code. Keep benchmark/{configs,judge,questions,scripts}
# indexed; only results/ is excluded.
benchmark/results/
